---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Medical Marijuana Doctor in Brandon FL | Releaf MD" 
  description="Visit Dr. Kelly Ennix King for your medical marijuana evaluation in Brandon, FL. Compassionate, professional, and veteran-led care."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-brand-mint py-16 lg:py-24 border-b border-brand-primary/10">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center space-y-4">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-primary/10 text-brand-primary rounded-full text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider">
        📍 Brandon, FL Clinic
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark leading-tight uppercase">Medical Marijuana Doctor Brandon FL</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Compassionate, physician-led assessments near Brandon Town Center. Get certified with Dr. Kelly Ennix King today.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-white border border-brand-primary/10 rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-12 shadow-whisper prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8">
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Your Trusted Brandon Medical Cannabis Clinic</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          If you are looking for a qualified medical marijuana doctor in Brandon, FL, Releaf MD provides a warm, cafe-style clinic environment focused on education and patient support. Led by Dr. Kelly Ennix King, a disabled Air Force veteran, our practice helps residents navigate the state registry process with confidence.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">What to Expect During Your Brandon Evaluation</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          State guidelines require an in-person clinical assessment for your initial certification. During your consultation, we keep things simple and structured:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li><strong>Review Medical History:</strong> Dr. Kelly reviews your diagnoses, treatments, and goals.</li>
          <li><strong>Confirm Qualifying Condition:</strong> We verify eligibility under Florida regulations.</li>
          <li><strong>Design Dosing Plan:</strong> Receive clear routes (smokable, oral, inhalation) and dosing guidance.</li>
          <li><strong>Registry Enrollment:</strong> We enter your certification into the state database immediately.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Office Location</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-700 font-bold mb-1">
              📍 935 Oakfield Dr. Brandon, FL 33511
            </p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
              Conveniently located to serve Brandon, Bloomingdale, and surrounding communities.
            </p>
            <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=935+Oakfield+Dr+Brandon+FL+33511" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block mt-2 text-xs font-bold text-brand-primary hover:underline">Get Directions &rarr;</a>
          </div>
          
          <div class="bg-brand-mint/40 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10">
            <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Hours of Operation</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
              <strong>Monday &ndash; Friday:</strong> 9 AM &ndash; 4 PM<br/>
              <strong>Saturday &ndash; Sunday:</strong> Closed<br/>
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-400 mt-1 block">(Hours may differ on public holidays)</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-brand-mint/20 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-brand-primary/10 my-6">
          <h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark text-sm mb-2">Adjacent Neighborhoods</h4>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 leading-relaxed">
            We also provide dedicated support and localized information for patients residing in nearby <a href="/locations/riverview-valrico" class="text-brand-accent font-bold hover:underline">Riverview and Valrico</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-serif-headline text-brand-dark">Why Choose Releaf MD?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
          Unlike large corporate "card mills" that rush you through assessments, Releaf MD offers a premium, personalized clinical experience:
        </p>

        <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">
          <li>No hidden fees or charges for changing routes of administration.</li>
          <li>Full 70-day orders to cover your active certification cycles.</li>
          <li>Private, respectful doctor consultations.</li>
        </ul>

        <div class="border-t border-slate-100 pt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4">
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 italic">
            Read our <a href="/florida-medical-marijuana-card-guide" class="text-brand-primary font-bold hover:underline">Complete Florida Card Guide</a>.
          </p>
          <a target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://live.vcita.com/site/DrKellyKing/online-scheduling?service=xnfeicu6jent0179" class="bg-brand-accent hover:bg-brand-primary text-white font-bold px-6 py-3 rounded-full text-xs uppercase transition-colors shadow-md active-press">
            Schedule Appointment
          </a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
